    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a bit of a mixed bag then. But if we're talking geopolitics, wouldn't you say the whole thing was a failure? I mean, if it just led to more instability and extremism in the region, doesn't that make the entire decision to intervene a strategic mistake regardless of the humanitarian stuff?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
